summary:
I am a Polyvalent geoscientist, with professional experience in rock physics and structural geology, basin analysis and sedimentology. Conducting regional to prospect scale evaluations. Of particular interest is the 4D evolution of geological systems at different time- and space- scale.

Some of my main activities consist of: numerical modelling, analogue modeling, seismic interpretation,  data compilation, reservoir analysis, tectonic reconstruction. I also have a large experience in organising Lab and field activities.

Science, history, traveling and biking remain my primary passions in life.
